        <title>Interpreting velocity graphs</title>
        <question>
            <para>Describe the motion corresponding to the following graph and plot the position vs time and acceleration vs time assuming the initial position is <number>0</number>:</para>
                <pspicture>
                  <code>(-1.5,-4)(5,4.3) 
