            </unit_number>high. A ball Y of mass 
            <latex>2m</latex> is projected vertically downwards from the same bridge at a speed of 
            <latex>{u}_{y}</latex>. The two balls reach the water at the same speed. Air friction can be
            ignored.</para>
            <para>Which of the following is true with reference to the speeds with which the balls are
            projected?</para>
            <list list-type="enumerated">
              <item>
